---
layout: base
title: Corrections
description: "A record of corrections made to published articles."
permalink: /corrections/
---

<div class="container" style="max-width: var(--max-width-prose); padding-block: var(--space-16);">
  <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: var(--text-3xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Corrections</h1>
  <p style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
    When we get something wrong, we fix it and note it here.
  </p>

  {% set correctedArticles = collections.correctionsLog %}
  {% if correctedArticles.length == 0 %}
  <p style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); font-style: italic;">No corrections on record.</p>
  {% else %}
  <div class="flow" style="--flow-space: var(--space-8);">
    {% for article in correctedArticles %}
    <article style="padding-bottom: var(--space-6); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-headline); font-size: var(--text-md);">
        <a href="{{ article.url }}" style="color: var(--color-ink);">{{ article.data.title }}</a>
      </h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-ink-faint); font-size: var(--text-sm);">
        {{ article.data.section }} &middot; Published {{ article.date | readableDate }}
      </p>
      <ul style="list-style: none; margin-top: var(--space-3);">
        {% for correction in article.data.corrections %}
        <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2); padding-left: var(--space-4); border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent); font-size: var(--text-sm);">
          <time datetime="{{ correction.date }}" style="color: var(--color-ink-faint); display: block;">{{ correction.date }}</time>
          {{ correction.description }}
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}
</div>
